Thinking a lot about humanity today...Thinking the world would be a better place if relationships and general human interaction were less about Give&take and more about Give&Giveback. 
Giving is truly powerful. When we give without expectation: receivers AND givers feel noticed, appreciated, happy, loved, & empowered. 
Do what you can to be more selfless today then observe how it positively affects those around you. 💜🤗 ( relating to this photo...I'm still loving this shoot with @clairethoringtonportraits 😍)
